    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克选举后动乱造成死亡人数升至 261 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/mozambique-death-toll-rises-to-261-in-post-election-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地观察组织称，莫桑比克选举后骚乱造成的死亡人数已上升至 261 人，其中大部分是被警方枪击造成的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/mozambique-death-toll-rises-to-261-in-post-election-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 11:45:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电缆受损后爱沙尼亚派船守护电力线路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/estonia-sends-ship-to-guard-power-link-after-cables-go-offline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前一天，芬兰扣押了一艘油轮，该油轮涉嫌用船锚损坏了五条电缆，这是大约一年内发生的第三起此类事件。爱沙尼亚随后派遣一艘海军舰艇巡逻一条海底电力线路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/estonia-sends-ship-to-guard-power-link-after-cables-go-offline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 10:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦议院解散后，德国将于 2 月举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/german-president-dissolves-parliament-and-calls-feb-23-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总统弗兰克-瓦尔特·施泰因迈尔解散议会，并将该国提前大选定于 2 月 23 日举行，正式批准了总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨提出的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/german-president-dissolves-parliament-and-calls-feb-23-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 10:01:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国对哈西娜展开新调查，印度请求引渡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/bangladesh-targets-hasina-with-new-probe-india-extradition-plea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国在对前被罢免领导人谢赫哈西娜的腐败调查中增加了新的指控，并向印度施压，要求将她引渡到该国接受指控，此举可能进一步加剧这两个南亚国家之间的关系紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/bangladesh-targets-hasina-with-new-probe-india-extradition-plea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 07:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
